The purpose of my role at State Trustees was to provide a high level of recruitment support to Line Managers and Team Leaders across the business, to ensure the right people were placed in the right positions. Some key responsibilities are as follows:

Provide advice, coaching and support to Managers and Team Leaders in areas such as candidate sourcing, candidate screening/testing/assessments, the preparation and conducting of interviews and reference checks;
